  "text": "Musleh et al. [CITATION_1] demonstrated an RDMA SR-IOV virtualization solution targeting InfiniBand networks, with an overall performance overhead of 15-30% compared to native performance. Also in [CITATION_2] authors analyzed the SR-IOV virtualization impact on HPC field, with evaluation results for applications based on MPI and Unified Parallel C paradigms.",
